snippet.title: Norfolk Warriors - Beta Demo v0 1 4
snippet.description: This is the first video of Norfolk Warriors Beta available at the Microsoft Store. Norfolk Warriors is a virtual tabletop turn based strategy game set in the Veil of Entropy Universe. It's developed using the Cohorts Game System, a proprietary game system designed and created by Mouchet Software Corp.
